### `Cargo.toml`

This project requires dependencies for async runtime (`tokio`), HTTP requests (`reqwest`), JSON handling (`serde`), and environment variables (`dotenv`).

```toml
[package]
name = "weather-cli"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
clap = { version = "4.4.11", features = ["derive"] }
dotenv = "0.15.0"
reqwest = { version = "0.11", features = ["json"] }
serde = { version = "1.0", features = ["derive"] }
serde_json = "1.0"
tokio = { version = "1", features = ["full"] }
